description.displayText: Janete has worked for us for about six months and we are extremely happy with her work. She is eager to learn, up for any challenge, and always a vibrant, happy personality. She shows up on time every day and works hard while she's here. But the best thing I can say about Janete is that she is extremely compassionate and truly cares for her patients and their well-being.
